2) program to reverse order of words

program to reverse order of words
i/p - > I am happy
o/p -> happy amm i

s="I am happy"
l1=[]
l=s.split()
print(len(l))
i=len(l)-1
print(i)
while i>=0:
    l1.append(l[i])
    i=i-1
output = ' '.join(l1)
print(output)
